            <div class="book-title">Book Title 5</div>
            <div class="book-author">Author 5</div>
            <div class="book-description">
                Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Nullam auctor, justo et bibendum efficitur, ex tortor a ex.
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

</div>


